Package: SkiPasses
Type: Package
Title: Toy Example Database
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Derek Sonderegger
Maintainer: The package maintainer <derek.sonderegger@gmail.com>
Description: This is a toy example for a teaching. It simulates a ski area
